                                            Locations
                                            
                                        


Adient Burscheid Development Center                                






























Situated near Düsseldorf and Cologne, our Burscheid Development Center serves as our European headquarters. This 14,500-square-meter facility has everything we need to stay a step ahead – from product development, industrial design and engineering to benchmarking, prototyping and consumer and market research. Even a dedicated area for sound, comfort and safety testing. With approximately 1,400 designers, engineers and product experts from more than 40 countries, it’s well-equipped to deliver the world-class seating components and systems that major automakers demand – and that Adient delivers.







Adient Ltd. & Co. KG
