Apr 28 17
Adient plc (NYSE:ADNT) is looking for acquisitions. The company's Chairman & Chief Executive Officer, Bruce McDonald, calling Asia a "more fragmented" market than United States and Europe, said that a potential acquisition might be possible in such regions.


