adient plc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Automotive
Sub-Industry: Auto Parts
Adient plc is a automotive seating supplier that designs, develops, manufactures, and distributes complete seat systems and their various components. The Company provides its products to the global auto industry for use in vans, pick-up trucks and SUV vehicles.




